title: Ep - 72 - Dr. Drew Pinsky
description:
Dr. Drew Pinsky is a practicing physician, Board Certified in Internal Medicine, and Board Certified in Addiction Medicine. He gives insight into the mind of a reality television star. 


Comedy writer and actress LaKendra Tookes reviews the season premiere of Real Housewives of Atlanta. 


Matchmaking expert Susan Trombetti discusses the season premiere of Marriage Bootcamp: Reality Stars. 


Reality Life with Kate Casey
